(5501, 388, 'about_short_desc', '<p>Welcome to RCDF, a non-profit organization dedicated to enhancing the lives of children up to 12 years old living with Autism Spectrum Disorders, ADHD, and Down syndrome, along with their families.</p>\r\n<p>From speech and language therapy to occupational therapy, Autism Vocational Interventions, educational interventions, behaviour therapy, and physical therapy, we strive to provide holistic support.Our commitment extends beyond individual care to encompass the entire community. Join us in our journey to make a meaningful difference in the lives of those we serve.</p>'),
