(19, 1, '2024-04-03 10:58:31', '2024-04-03 10:58:31', 'RCD Memorial Foundation, hereinafter referred to as \"the Foundation,\" is committed to ensuring the privacy and security of all personal information collected through our payment gateway for donations. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect donor data.\r\n\r\nCollection of Personal Information:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>When you make a donation through our payment gateway, we may collect personal details such as your name, email address, postal address, phone number, and payment information (e.g., credit card details). This information is collected solely for the purpose of processing your donation and providing our services. They will not be shared with any third parties except as required by law.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nUse of Personal Information:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Your personal information is used solely for processing your donation and communicating with you regarding your donation, including providing donation receipts and acknowledging your support. We do not use donor information for any other purposes without your explicit consent. Your health-related data will never be disclosed without your explicit consent. We respect your privacy rights and will only use your personal information for the intended purposes as stated in this Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAccess and Removal of Personal Information\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>You have the right to request access to the personal information we hold about you. If you wish to review or remove any personal data, please contact us, and we will promptly address your request. Additionally, you can update your personal information with us in case of any changes.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nSecurity Measures\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Foundation employs industry-standard security measures to protect the confidentiality and integrity of your personal information. All payment transactions are encrypted using Secure Socket Layer (SSL) technology, and our payment gateway complies with Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard (PCI DSS) requirements.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThird-Party Service Providers\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>In order to process donations and maintain our payment gateway, the Foundation may engage third-party service providers. These service providers are contractually obligated to maintain the confidentiality and security of donor information and are only permitted to use the information for the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nDonor Rights\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Donors have the right to request access to the personal information we hold about them and to request corrections or updates to their information. Donors also have the right to opt out of receiving communications from the Foundation at any time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nChanges to Privacy Policy:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Foundation reserves the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be effective immediately upon posting on our website.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nConsent\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>By making a donation through our payment gateway, you consent to the collection, use, and processing of your personal information in accordance with this Privacy Policy.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nConfidentiality and Data Protection\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>RCD Memorial Foundation maintains the confidentiality of your personal details, financial information, sexual identity, and medical concerns in compliance with the Data Protection Act of India. We employ appropriate security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nBy using our services, you consent to the collection and use of your personal information as described in this Privacy Policy. We reserve the right to update or modify this policy at any time, and any changes will be effective upon posting on our website. Please review this Privacy Policy periodically for updates.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions or concerns regarding our Privacy Policy or the handling of your personal information, please contact us.', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'privacy-policy', '', '', '2024-04-24 08:21:18', '2024-04-24 08:21:18', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/?page_id=19', 0, 'page', '', 0),
