(210, 1, '2024-01-08 08:06:33', '2024-01-08 08:06:33', 'On a cool December morning of 2023 we all at RCD Memorial went to Bhasa Pull to spend an entire day with each other. The event was a celebration of love, unity, and togetherness with our kids and their parents showing great enthusiasm.\r\n\r\nParents were delighted to see their children immersed in activities designed to their interests and abilities, creating memories that will be cherished for years to come. It was a day of respite and relaxation, providing families with an opportunity to connect, share stories, and support one another on their journeys.\r\n\r\nThe picnic exemplified our commitment to creating inclusive spaces where all individuals feel valued, accepted, and celebrated for who they are. It was a testament to the power of community and the profound impact of coming together to uplift and empower one another.\r\n\r\nAs the sun set on a day filled with laughter and joy, our hearts were full, knowing that we had created a meaningful experience for our special children and their families. We look forward to many more opportunities to create moments of happiness and connection in the future.', 'Embracing joy in the lap of nature: Picnic 2023', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'embracing-joy-in-the-lap-of-nature-picnic-2023', '', '', '2024-04-23 11:44:54', '2024-04-23 11:44:54', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/?post_type=event&#038;p=210', 0, 'event', '', 0),
