(292, 1, '2024-04-10 10:32:17', '2024-04-10 10:32:17', 'Occupational therapy is meant to make daily living easier. Occupational therapy intervention employs everyday activities to enhance health, well-being, and the kid’s capacity to engage in significant life activities like writing, tying shoes, using scissors, bathing, getting dressed, etc.\r\n\r\nThe techniques used seem like play but they are specifically designed to target areas of difficulty and delay. Our occupational therapists collaborate with children and their families to devise customized OT plans by utilizing assessment tools for achieving educational objectives.', 'Occupational Therapy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'occupational-therapy', '', '', '2024-04-22 12:16:28', '2024-04-22 12:16:28', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/service/services-1-copy/', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(293, 1, '2024-04-10 10:32:18', '2024-04-10 10:32:18', 'This refers to programs, strategies, and supports specially designed to help individuals with Autism Spectrum Disorder find and maintain employment. This intervention is aimed at addressing the unique challenges that individuals with ASD may face in the workplace, such as social communication difficulties, sensory sensitivities, and executive functioning impairments.', 'Autism Vocational Intervention', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'autism-vocational-intervention', '', '', '2024-04-22 12:16:44', '2024-04-22 12:16:44', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/service/services-1-copy-2/', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(294, 1, '2024-04-10 10:32:20', '2024-04-10 10:32:20', 'Evidence-based treatment for children to address their unique needs encompasses a range of approaches. We employ positive reinforcement techniques to instil new behaviours and address any existing behavioural issues. Rooted in behaviourism\'s core principle that behaviours are learned and modifiable through conditioning, our approach focuses on effective behaviour change.', 'Specialized Behavioural Therapies', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'specialized-behavioural-therapies', '', '', '2024-04-22 12:23:08', '2024-04-22 12:23:08', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/service/services-1-copy-3/', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(295, 1, '2024-04-10 10:32:22', '2024-04-10 10:32:22', 'Physiotherapy for children with special needs involves tailored exercises and activities to improve mobility, strength, and coordination. It also supports emotional and psychological development, fostering independence and enhancing quality of life.', 'Physical Therapy', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'physical-therapy', '', '', '2024-04-22 12:23:48', '2024-04-22 12:23:48', '', 0, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/service/services-1-copy-4/', 0, 'service', '', 0),
