(436, 1, '2024-04-22 11:03:42', '2024-04-22 11:03:42', 'This refers to programs, strategies, and supports specially designed to help individuals with Autism Spectrum Disorder find and maintain employment. This intervention is aimed at addressing the unique challenges that individuals with ASD may face in the workplace, such as social communication difficulties, sensory sensitivities, and executive functioning impairments.', 'Autism Vocational Intervention', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '293-autosave-v1', '', '', '2024-04-22 11:03:42', '2024-04-22 11:03:42', '', 293, 'https://rcdngo.artemisys.com/?p=436', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
